{"title_page": "Fawzi Benkhalidi", "text_new": "{{short description|Algerian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Fawzi Benkhalidi\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1963|02|03|df=y}}\n| birth_place    = [[Algeria]]\n| death_date     = \n| height         = \n| position       = [[Midfielder#Attacking midfielder|Attacking midfielder]]\n| years1         = {{0|0000}}\u20131986 | clubs1 = [[Olympique de M\u00e9d\u00e9a]] | caps1 = |goals1 = \n| years2         = 1986\u20131987       | clubs2 = [[WA Boufarik]]| caps2 = |goals2 = \n| years3         = 1987\u20131990       | clubs3 = [[USM Alger]]  | caps3 = |goals3 = \n| years4         = 1990\u20131992       | clubs4 = [[Olympique de M\u00e9d\u00e9a]] | caps4 = |goals4 = \n| years5         = 1992\u20131994       | clubs5 = [[USM Alger]]  | caps5 = |goals5 = \n| nationalyears1 = 1984\u20131986\n| nationalteam1  = [[Algeria national football team|Algeria]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 10\n| nationalgoals1 = 2\n}}\n\n'''Fawzi Benkhalidi''' (born 3 February 1963) is an [[Algeria]]n [[association football|football]] [[Forward (association football)|forward]] who played for [[Algeria national football team|Algeria]] in the [[1986 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>[https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/edition=68/teams/team=43843.html 1986 FIFA World Cup Mexico] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111003011244/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/edition%3D68/teams/team%3D43843.html |date=2011-10-03 }}</ref> He also played for [[WA Boufarik]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/statisticsandrecords/players/player=46456/index.html FIFA profile]\n\n{{Algeria squad 1986 African Cup of Nations}}\n{{Algeria Squad 1986 World Cup}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Benkhalidi, Faouzi}}\n[[Category:1963 births]]\n[[Category:Algerian footballers]]\n[[Category:Algeria international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:1986 African Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:1986 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Olympique de M\u00e9d\u00e9a players]]\n[[Category:USM Alger players]]\n[[Category:WA Boufarik players]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Fawzi Benkhalidi\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1963|02|03|df=y}}\n| birth_place    = [[Algeria]]\n| death_date     = \n| height         = \n| position       = [[Midfielder#Attacking midfielder|Attacking midfielder]]\n| years1         = {{0|0000}}\u20131986 | clubs1 = [[Olympique de M\u00e9d\u00e9a]] | caps1 = |goals1 = \n| years2         = 1986\u20131987       | clubs2 = [[WA Boufarik]]| caps2 = |goals2 = \n| years3         = 1987\u20131990       | clubs3 = [[USM Alger]]  | caps3 = |goals3 = \n| years4         = 1990\u20131992       | clubs4 = [[Olympique de M\u00e9d\u00e9a]] | caps4 = |goals4 = \n| years5         = 1992\u20131994       | clubs5 = [[USM Alger]]  | caps5 = |goals5 = \n| nationalyears1 = 1984\u20131986\n| nationalteam1  = [[Algeria national football team|Algeria]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 10\n| nationalgoals1 = 2\n}}\n\n'''Fawzi Benkhalidi''' (born 3 February 1963) is an [[Algeria]]n [[association football|football]] [[Forward (association football)|forward]] who played for [[Algeria national football team|Algeria]] in the [[1986 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>[https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/edition=68/teams/team=43843.html 1986 FIFA World Cup Mexico] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111003011244/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/edition%3D68/teams/team%3D43843.html |date=2011-10-03 }}</ref> He also played for [[WA Boufarik]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/statisticsandrecords/players/player=46456/index.html FIFA profile]\n\n{{Algeria squad 1986 African Cup of Nations}}\n{{Algeria Squad 1986 