o-we-are/honorary-fellows NFTS Honorary Fellowship]\n| Outstanding Contribution to the British Film and Television Industry\n| \u2013\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2011\n| [[British Academy of Film and Television Arts|BAFTA]]: [[Britannia Awards|Britannia Award (Los Angeles)]]\n| John Schlesinger Britannia Award for Excellence in Directing\n| ''Harry Potter''<br />{{small|''Order of the Phoenix'', ''Half-Blood Prince'', ''Deathly Hallows''}}\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award]]\n| Best Director\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows \u2013 Part 1''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[2011 Scream Awards|Scream Award]]\n| Best Director\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows \u2013 Part 2''\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2012\n| [[Saturn Award]]\n| Best Director\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows \u2013 Part 2''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[SFX (magazine)|SFX Award]]\n| Best Director\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows \u2013 Part 2''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Empire Awards|Empire Award]]\n| Best Director\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows \u2013 Part 2''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[University of Essex]]\n| Honorary Degree\n| \u2013\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|2016\n|| [[British Academy of Film and Television Arts|BAFTA]]: [[British Academy Film Awards|British Academy Film Award]]\n|Outstanding British Film\n|''[[Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them (film)|Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Reception==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Film\n! [[Rotten Tomatoes]]<ref>{{cite web | title=David Yates | url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/celebrity/david_yates | website=Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate=2 May 2019}}</ref>\n! [[Metacritic]]<ref>{{cite web | title=David Yates |url=https://www.metacritic.com/person/david-yates | website=Metacritic |accessdate=22 December 2018}}</ref>\n! [[CinemaScore]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.cinemascore.com/ | title=CinemaScore | work=cinemascore.com | accessdate=22 December 2018}}</ref>\n! Bu