{"title_page": "Billal Ouali", "text_new": "{{short description|Algerian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name = Billal Ouali\n|image = \n|fullname = \n|birth_date  = {{Birth date and age|1987|5|15}}\n|birth_place = [[M'Sila]], [[Algeria]]\n|height = \n|position = [[Striker (association football)|Striker]]\n|currentclub = [[MO B\u00e9ja\u00efa]]\n|clubnumber = 21\n|youthyears1 = \n|youthclubs1 = \n|years1 = 2005\u20132012\n|clubs1 = [[Paradou AC]]\n|caps1 = -\n|goals1 = -\n|years2 = 2011\u20132012\n|clubs2 = \u2192 [[JSM B\u00e9ja\u00efa]] (loan)\n|caps2 = 24\n|goals2 = 1  \n|years3 = 2012\u20132015\n|clubs3 = [[MC Alger]]\n|caps3 = 47\n|goals3 = 0  \n|years4 = 2015\u20132018\n|clubs4 = [[NA Hussein Dey]]\n|caps4 = /\n|goals4 = 0  \n|years5 = 2018\u2013\n|clubs5 = [[MO B\u00e9ja\u00efa]]\n|caps5 = /\n|goals5 = 0  \n|pcupdate = 00:00, May 13, 2015 (EST) \n}}\n\n'''Billal Ouali''' (born May 15, 1987 in [[M'Sila]]) is an [[Algeria]]n football player who is currently playing as a forward for [[MO B\u00e9ja\u00efa]] in the [[Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 2]].\n\n==Club career==\nIn August 2007, he was handed a trial with [[Ligue 1]] side [[OGC Nice]] but he failed to impress the coach .<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nationscup.mtnfootball.com/live/content.php?Item_ID=10794&Revision=en%2F2|title=Two Rejected At Nice Trials|accessdate=July 19, 2011}} {{Dead link|date=April 2015}}</ref>\n\nOn July 14, 2011, Ouali was loaned out to [[JSM B\u00e9ja\u00efa]] for one season.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.djazairess.com/fr/lebuteur/40273|title=JSMB: Pr\u00eat\u00e9 pour un an \u00e0 la JSMB : Ouali premi\u00e8re recrue|accessdate=April 20, 2011}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20120212122518/http://www.dzfoot.com/joueur.php?joueur_id=1285&saison_id=13 DZfoot Profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ouali, Billal}}\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Algerian footballers]]\n[[Category:Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1 player