12122518/http://www.dzfoot.com/joueur.php?joueur_id=1285&saison_id=13 DZfoot Profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ouali, Billal}}\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Algerian footballers]]\n[[Category:Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1 players]]\n[[Category:Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 2 players]]\n[[Category:JSM B\u00e9ja\u00efa players]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from M'Sila]]\n[[Category:Paradou AC players]]\n[[Category:MC Alger players]]\n\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n{{Algeria-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Algerian footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"Algerian footballer\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Billal_Ouali"}
